## Environment Variables Template for Vercel Deployment

## AI & Embeddings
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here
EMBEDDING_API_KEY=your_huggingface_api_key_here

## App URL (update with your Vercel deployment URL)
NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://your-app.vercel.app

## Supabase (Required for Vercel)
SUPABASE_URL=your_supabase_project_url
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your_supabase_service_role_key

## MySQL Configuration
## ⚠️ DO NOT SET THESE ON VERCEL - MySQL requires VPN and only works locally
## When these are not set on Vercel, the app will automatically use Supabase cache
## Only set these in your local .env.local file
# MYSQL_HOST=your_mysql_host
# MYSQL_PORT=3306
# MYSQL_USER=your_mysql_user
# MYSQL_PASSWORD=your_mysql_password
# MYSQL_DATABASE=your_database_name
